	<div id="path" class="py-12 overflow-hidden bg-gray-900 sm:pt-20">
		<div class="px-6 mx-auto max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
			<div class="grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 mx-auto gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="lg:pt-4 lg:pr-8">
				<div class="lg:max-w-lg">
				<h2 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400 text-base/7">
					How we work together
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white text-pretty sm:text-5xl">
					Your Path Forward
				</p>
				<p class="mt-6 text-gray-300 text-lg/8">
                    You don't need a 12-step program. <br class="hidden sm:block">You need clarity, then action. Here's how it works:
                </p>
				<dl class="max-w-xl mt-10 space-y-8 text-gray-400 text-base/7 lg:max-w-none">
					<div class="relative pl-9">
						<dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-slot="icon" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute text-indigo-400 top-1 left-1 size-5">
								<path d="M5.5 17a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-1.44-8.765 4.5 4.5 0 0 1 8.302-3.046 3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.504 4.272A4 4 0 0 1 15 17H5.5Zm3.75-2.75a.75.75 0 0 0 1.5 0V9.66l1.95 2.1a.75.75 0 1 0 1.1-1.02l-3.25-3.5a.75.75 0 0 0-1.1 0l-3.25 3.5a.75.75 0 1 0 1.1 1.02l1.95-2.1v4.59Z" clip-rule="evenodd" fill-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							Clarity
						</dt>
						<dd class="inline">
                            We figure out what's actually wrong
                            Not the symptoms. Not the surface stuff. The real problem. Sometimes you already know it. Sometimes we discover it together. Either way, we start with truth.
						</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="relative pl-9">
						<dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-slot="icon" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute text-indigo-400 top-1 left-1 size-5">
								<path d="M10 1a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-4.5 4.5V9H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-.5V5.5A4.5 4.5 0 0 0 10 1Zm3 8V5.5a3 3 0 1 0-6 0V9h6Z" clip-rule="evenodd" fill-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							Strategy
						</dt>
						<dd class="inline">
							We build the plan
                            Now that we know what needs to change, we map it out. What gets built? What gets said? What gets fixed first? You'll have a clear path forward - no guessing, no vague advice.
						</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="relative pl-9">
						<dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-slot="icon" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute text-indigo-400 top-1 left-1 size-5">
								<path d="M10 1a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-4.5 4.5V9H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-.5V5.5A4.5 4.5 0 0 0 10 1Zm3 8V5.5a3 3 0 1 0-6 0V9h6Z" clip-rule="evenodd" fill-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
							Execution
						</dt>
						<dd class="inline">
							We make it real
                            This is where most people stop. Not us. We build the thing, write the speech, fix the system, launch the site. You get something tangible - something that works.
						</dd>
					</div>
					<div class="relative pl-9">
						<dt class="inline font-semibold text-white">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" data-slot="icon" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute text-indigo-400 top-1 left-1 size-5">
								<path d="M4.632 3.533A2 2 0 0 1 6.577 2h6.846a2 2 0 0 1 1.945 1.533l1.976 8.234A3.489 3.489 0 0 0 16 11.5H4c-.476 0-.93.095-1.344.267l1.976-8.234Z" />
