							</svg>
							Growth
						</dt>
						<dd class="inline">
							You keep moving
                            The goal isn't just solving today's problem. It's giving you the tools and confidence to solve the next one faster. You don't just get results - you become more capable.
						</dd>
					</div>
				</dl>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative pt-12 lg:pt-16">
				<img src="/images/personal-development-journey.png" alt="Product screenshot" class="shadow-xl rounded-xl ring-1 ring-white/10 md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0" />
			</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
    